test: You do not make a farm next to the water.
ulamakni man kubamhma yaihnit yak buitaman
My master does not open the owls’ book next to the moon.
man wakimasa talasyangna yang walakibis balna taanitna yak
You do not see the spider’s pencil next to his masters.
yang dakiwan ulamak balna mukus balna yayamwaski witingna yaninamak taanit yak
Our masters do not open the clouds in front of us.
man kisauri kakaswi yang dangkit yak
You make the dog’s raft next to the water.
kuring man sumalu balna kisauri kakaswi yang dangkit yak
I shake pencils above your.PL grandmother.
man walamabis yang titinghki wakisa talwi balna yaihnitna yak
You.PL do not eat our bananas at a raft.
